OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHosepipe ban extends to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F390,000 homes              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A hosepipe ban has come into force     
OL,6, across large parts of Devon.           
OL,8,FSouth West Water (SWW) said the        
OL,9,Fextended restriction would help        
OL,10,Freplenish water supplies at Roadford   
OL,11,Freservoir ahead of the summer.         
OL,13,FThe utility said about 390,000 homes in
OL,14,FDevon would be affected by the latest  
OL,15,Frestriction.                           
OL,17,FAn initial ban, which is still in place
OL,18,Fafter being introduced in August 2022, 
OL,19,Fcovers Cornwall and a small part of    
OL,20,Fnorth Devon.                           
